{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312040253ad051bc281fc4aff","session_id":"5a4189c6-c669-4ea4-8c81-fee95bc26849","message":{"id":"20260312040253ad051bc281fc4aff","content":[{"type":"text","text":"spec.md 已创建，需求清晰无模糊点。继续 Step 2。\n\n## Step 2: prizmkit.plan → plan.md"}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde7d5b3127935cc6935ad960a6b2","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:04:15.387Z","_requestId":"8c83b89fde8941858aa97e5b6b7114a4"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312040253ad051bc281fc4aff","session_id":"5a4189c6-c669-4ea4-8c81-fee95bc26849","message":{"id":"20260312040253ad051bc281fc4aff","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_fd2adb85b59a4067b79e19d9","name":"Write","input":{"content":"# F-005: Pipeline Status Aggregation and Log Streaming — Technical Plan\n\n## 1. Architecture Overview\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                         Telegram Command Router (F-002)                      │\n│                    src/bot/commands/handlers/*.js                            │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                    │                          │\n                    ▼                          ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n│   Enhanced Status Handler   │  │   Enhanced Logs Handler     │\n│   src/bot/commands/         │  │   src/bot/commands/         │\n│   handlers/status.js        │  │   handlers/logs.js          │\n│   (MODIFIED)                │  │   (MODIFIED)                │\n└─────────────────────────────┘  └─────────────────────────────┘\n                    │                          │\n                    └──────────────┬───────────┘\n                                   ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    Pipeline Status Aggregator (NEW)                          │\n│                    src/services/pipeline-status-aggregator.js                │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n│  │ • aggregateStatus(type)      • getStatistics(type)                  │    │\n│  │ • getErrorSummary(type)      • formatStatusMessage(status)          │    │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                                   │\n                    ┌──────────────┼──────────────┐\n                    ▼              ▼              ▼\n┌─────────────────┐ ┌─────────────────────┐ ┌─────────────────────┐\n│ Pipeline        │ │ Message Chunker     │ │ Log Pager           │\n│ Controller      │ │ (NEW)               │ │ (NEW)               │\n│ (F-004)         │ │ src/utils/          │ │ src/utils/          │\n│                 │ │ message-chunker.js  │ │ log-pager.js        │\n└─────────────────┘ └─────────────────────┘ └─────────────────────┘\n\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                      Pipeline Notifier Service (NEW)                         │\n│                    src/services/pipeline-notifier.js                         │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n│  │ • startHeartbeat(config)     • stopHeartbeat()                      │    │\n│  │ • notifyStart(type)          • notifyComplete(type, result)         │    │\n│  │ • notifyError(type, error)   • notifyProgress(type, progress)       │    │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                    │\n                    ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                         Telegram Bot Instance                                │\n│                         src/bot/telegram.js                                  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. Component Design\n\n### 2.1 Pipeline Status Aggregator (`src/services/pipeline-status-aggregator.js`)\n\n**职责**: 从多个状态源聚合信息，生成完整的状态视图\n\n**核心方法**:\n\n```javascript\nexport function createPipelineStatusAggregator(options = {}) {\n  const {\n    stateManager = getDefaultStateManager(),\n    lockManager = getDefaultLockManager(),\n    config = loadPipelineInfraConfig()\n  } = options;\n\n  return {\n    /**\n     * Aggregate full status for a pipeline type.\n     * @param {'feature' | 'bugfix'} type\n     * @returns {Promise<AggregatedStatus>}\n     */\n    async aggregateStatus(type),\n\n    /**\n     * Get statistics summary.\n     * @param {'feature' | 'bugfix'} type\n     * @returns {Promise<StatisticsSummary>}\n     */\n    async getStatistics(type),\n\n    /**\n     * Get recent error summary.\n     * @param {'feature' | 'bugfix'} type\n     * @param {number} maxLength - Max error message length\n     * @returns {Promise<ErrorSummary | null>}\n     */\n    async getErrorSummary(type, maxLength = 200),\n\n    /**\n     * Format status for Telegram display.\n     * @param {AggregatedStatus} status\n     * @returns {string} Formatted message\n     */\n    formatStatusMessage(status)\n  };\n}\n```\n\n**数据模型**:\n\n```typescript\ninterface AggregatedStatus {\n  ok: boolean;\n  type: 'feature' | 'bugfix';\n  phase: 'idle' | 'running' | 'paused' | 'completed' | 'failed';\n  message: string;\n\n  // Running info\n  isRunning: boolean;\n  pid?: number;\n  currentTarget?: {\n    id: string;\n    name?: string;\n    startedAt: string;\n    elapsed?: number; // seconds\n  };\n\n  // Statistics\n  statistics: {\n    total: number;\n    completed: number;\n    failed: number;\n    skipped: number;\n    pending: number;\n  };\n\n  // Last result (if not running)\n  lastResult?: {\n    runId: string;\n    completedAt: string;\n    status: 'success' | 'failed' | 'partial';\n    duration?: number; // seconds\n  };\n\n  // Error info\n  lastError?: {\n    targetId: string;\n    message: string;\n    timestamp: string;\n  };\n\n  // Lock info\n  lockInfo?: {\n    pid: number;\n    acquiredAt: string;\n  };\n}\n\ninterface StatisticsSummary {\n  total: number;\n  completed: number;\n  failed: number;\n  skipped: number;\n  pending: number;\n  successRate: number; // percentage\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2.2 Message Chunker (`src/utils/message-chunker.js`)\n\n**职责**: 将长消息分段，确保在行边界切分，遵守 Telegram 消息长度限制\n\n**核心方法**:\n\n```javascript\nexport const TELEGRAM_MESSAGE_LIMIT = 4096;\nexport const SAFE_MESSAGE_LIMIT = 4000; // 留出 markdown 和缓冲\n\n/**\n * Chunk a message into parts that fit Telegram's limit.\n * @param {string} content - Content to chunk\n * @param {Object} options - Options\n * @param {number} [options.limit=4000] - Max chars per chunk\n * @param {boolean} [options.respectLineBounds=true] - Split at line boundaries\n * @returns {string[]} Array of chunks\n */\nexport function chunkMessage(content, options = {}) {\n  const { limit = SAFE_MESSAGE_LIMIT, respectLineBounds = true } = options;\n\n  if (content.length <= limit) {\n    return [content];\n  }\n\n  if (!respectLineBounds) {\n    return chunkByChars(content, limit);\n  }\n\n  return chunkByLines(content, limit);\n}\n\n/**\n * Chunk content by lines, respecting line boundaries.\n */\nfunction chunkByLines(content, limit) {\n  const lines = content.split('\\n');\n  const chunks = [];\n  let currentChunk = '';\n\n  for (const line of lines) {\n    if ((currentChunk + '\\n' + line).length > limit) {\n      if (currentChunk) {\n        chunks.push(currentChunk);\n        currentChunk = line;\n      } else {\n        // Single line exceeds limit - split by chars\n        chunks.push(line.slice(0, limit));\n        currentChunk = line.slice(limit);\n      }\n    } else {\n      currentChunk = currentChunk ? currentChunk + '\\n' + line : line;\n    }\n  }\n\n  if (currentChunk) {\n    chunks.push(currentChunk);\n  }\n\n  return chunks;\n}\n\n/**\n * Send chunks with pagination labels.\n * @param {Function} reply - Telegram reply function\n * @param {string[]} chunks - Message chunks\n * @param {Object} options - Options\n * @param {string} [options.prefix=''] - Prefix for first message\n * @param {boolean} [options.codeBlock=true] - Wrap in code block\n */\nexport async function sendChunks(reply, chunks, options = {}) {\n  const { prefix = '', codeBlock = true } = options;\n  const total = chunks.length;\n\n  for (let i = 0; i < total; i++) {\n    const label = total > 1 ? `(${i + 1}/${total})\\n` : '';\n    let message = label + chunks[i];\n\n    if (codeBlock) {\n      message = `\\`\\`\\`\\n${message}\\n\\`\\`\\``;\n    }\n\n    if (i === 0 && prefix) {\n      message = prefix + '\\n' + message;\n    }\n\n    await reply(message);\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2.3 Log Pager (`src/utils/log-pager.js`)\n\n**职责**: 日志分页读取，支持偏移和行数限制\n\n**核心方法**:\n\n```javascript\nexport function createLogPager(options = {}) {\n  const { maxLines = 500 } = options;\n\n  return {\n    /**\n     * Read log with pagination.\n     * @param {string} logPath - Path to log file\n     * @param {Object} params - Pagination params\n     * @param {number} [params.lines=50] - Lines to read\n     * @param {number} [params.offset=0] - Offset from start (0-based)\n     * @returns {Promise<LogPage>}\n     */\n    async readPage(logPath, params = {}) {\n      const { lines = 50, offset = 0 } = params;\n      const actualLines = Math.min(lines, maxLines);\n\n      // Implementation...\n    },\n\n    /**\n     * Get total line count.\n     * @param {string} logPath - Path to log file\n     * @returns {Promise<number>}\n     */\n    async getTotalLines(logPath) {\n      // Implementation...\n    }\n  };\n}\n\ninterface LogPage {\n  ok: boolean;\n  content: string;\n  lines: string[];\n  pagination: {\n    offset: number;\n    count: number;\n    total: number;\n    hasMore: boolean;\n    nextOffset?: number;\n  };\n  logPath: string;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2.4 Pipeline Notifier (`src/services/pipeline-notifier.js`)\n\n**职责**: 主动推送管道事件到 Telegram\n\n**核心方法**:\n\n```javascript\nexport function createPipelineNotifier(options = {}) {\n  const {\n    bot,\n    chatId,\n    statusAggregator = createPipelineStatusAggregator(),\n    config = loadNotifierConfig()\n  } = options;\n\n  let heartbeatInterval = null;\n\n  return {\n    /**\n     * Start heartbeat notifications.\n     */\n    startHeartbeat(type, intervalMs = 300000) { // 5 min default\n\n    },\n\n    /**\n     * Stop heartbeat notifications.\n     */\n    stopHeartbeat() {\n\n    },\n\n    /**\n     * Notify pipeline started.\n     */\n    async notifyStart(type, info) {\n\n    },\n\n    /**\n     * Notify pipeline completed.\n     */\n    async notifyComplete(type, result) {\n\n    },\n\n    /**\n     * Notify target completed (optional).\n     */\n    async notifyTargetComplete(type, targetId) {\n\n    },\n\n    /**\n     * Notify error occurred.\n     */\n    async notifyError(type, error) {\n\n    },\n\n    /**\n     * Send message with retry.\n     */\n    async sendMessage(text, options = {}) {\n\n    }\n  };\n}\n```\n\n**配置**:\n\n```javascript\n// src/config.js extension\nexport const NOTIFIER_CONFIG = {\n  heartbeatIntervalMs: 300000, // 5 minutes\n  errorSummaryMaxLength: 300,\n  progressNotifyEnabled: false, // Per-target completion\n  retryAttempts: 3,\n  retryDelayMs: 1000\n};\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. Interface Design\n\n### 3.1 Status Command API\n\n#### `handleStatus(handlerCtx)`\n\n**Input**: Enhanced handler context\n\n```typescript\ninterface StatusHandlerContext {\n  params: {\n    type?: 'feature' | 'bugfix';\n    _args?: string[]; // Positional args\n  };\n  reply: (text: string, options?: SendMessageOptions) => Promise<void>;\n}\n```\n\n**Output**: Telegram message\n\n```\n📊 Pipeline Status: feature\n\nPhase: 🔄 Running\nPID: 12345\nCurrent: F-005 (Pipeline Status Aggregation)\nStarted: 2026-03-12 10:30:00\nElapsed: 15m 30s\n\n📈 Statistics:\n• Completed: 4/8\n• Failed: 1\n• Skipped: 0\n• Pending: 3\n\n❌ Last Error (F-003):\nConfiguration file not found: .env.local\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3.2 Logs Command API\n\n#### `handleLogs(handlerCtx)`\n\n**Input**: Enhanced handler context\n\n```typescript\ninterface LogsHandlerContext {\n  params: {\n    type?: 'feature' | 'bugfix';\n    lines?: number; // via --lines=N\n    offset?: number; // via --offset=N\n    _args?: string[];\n  };\n  reply: (text: string) => Promise<void>;\n  replyFile: (content: string, filename: string) => Promise<void>;\n}\n```\n\n**Output**: Telegram messages or file\n\n```\n📋 Logs (feature) — Lines 51-100 of 500\n\n[2026-03-12 10:31:00] INFO Starting F-004...\n[2026-03-12 10:31:05] INFO Reading state files...\n[2026-03-12 10:31:10] ERROR Failed to read config\n...\n\n📄 Navigate: /logs --offset=0 (first) | /logs --offset=100 (next)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3.3 Notifier Events\n\n#### Pipeline Start Event\n\n```\n🚀 Pipeline Started: feature\n\nRun ID: run-20260312103000\nTargets: 8\nMode: Daemon\nLog: /path/to/pipeline-daemon.log\n```\n\n#### Heartbeat Event\n\n```\n💓 Pipeline Heartbeat: feature\n\nCurrent: F-005\nElapsed: 15m 30s\nProgress: 4/8 completed, 1 failed\nStatus: Running normally\n```\n\n#### Error Event\n\n```\n⚠️ Target Failed: F-003\n\nStage: Configuration\nError: Configuration file not found: .env.local\n\n[View Full Log] (inline button)\n```\n\n#### Complete Event\n\n```\n✅ Pipeline Completed: feature\n\nStatus: Partial Success\nDuration: 45m 20s\nResults: 6 completed, 2 failed\n\nFailed Targets:\n• F-003: Configuration error\n• F-007: Timeout exceeded\n\n[View Details] (inline button)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. Data Model\n\n### 4.1 Status Aggregation Schema\n\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"feature\",\n  \"phase\": \"running\",\n  \"isRunning\": true,\n  \"pid\": 12345,\n  \"currentTarget\": {\n    \"id\": \"F-005\",\n    \"name\": \"Pipeline Status Aggregation\",\n    \"startedAt\": \"2026-03-12T10:30:00Z\",\n    \"elapsed\": 930\n  },\n  \"statistics\": {\n    \"total\": 8,\n    \"completed\": 4,\n    \"failed\": 1,\n    \"skipped\": 0,\n    \"pending\": 3\n  },\n  \"lastError\": {\n    \"targetId\": \"F-003\",\n    \"message\": \"Configuration file not found\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-12T10:15:30Z\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 4.2 Log Page Schema\n\n```json\n{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"content\": \"...\",\n  \"lines\": [\"line1\", \"line2\"],\n  \"pagination\": {\n    \"offset\": 50,\n    \"count\": 50,\n    \"total\": 500,\n    \"hasMore\": true,\n    \"nextOffset\": 100\n  },\n  \"logPath\": \"/path/to/pipeline-daemon.log\"\n}\n```\n\n### 4.3 Notifier Config Extension\n\n```javascript\n// .env or config\nNOTIFIER_HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_MS=300000\nNOTIFIER_ERROR_SUMMARY_MAX_LENGTH=300\nNOTIFIER_PROGRESS_NOTIFY_ENABLED=false\nNOTIFIER_RETRY_ATTEMPTS=3\nNOTIFIER_CHAT_ID=123456789\n```\n\n---\n\n## 5. Module Dependencies\n\n```\nstatus.js (modified)\n    ├── pipeline-status-aggregator.js (NEW)\n    │       ├── state-manager.js (F-004)\n    │       ├── lock-manager.js (F-004)\n    │       └── pipeline-controller.js (F-004)\n    └── message-chunker.js (NEW)\n\nlogs.js (modified)\n    ├── pipeline-controller.js (F-004)\n    ├── log-pager.js (NEW)\n    └── message-chunker.js (NEW)\n\npipeline-notifier.js (NEW)\n    ├── pipeline-status-aggregator.js (NEW)\n    ├── state-manager.js (F-004)\n    ├── message-chunker.js (NEW)\n    └── node-telegram-bot-api (external)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 6. Testing Strategy\n\n### 6.1 Unit Tests\n\n| Module | Test File | Focus |\n|--------|-----------|-------|\n| pipeline-status-aggregator.js | `tests/services/pipeline-status-aggregator.test.js` | Status aggregation, statistics calculation, error extraction |\n| message-chunker.js | `tests/utils/message-chunker.test.js` | Chunk size, line boundary handling, UTF-8 safety |\n| log-pager.js | `tests/utils/log-pager.test.js` | Pagination, offset handling, large file streaming |\n| pipeline-notifier.js | `tests/services/pipeline-notifier.test.js` | Heartbeat, error push, retry logic |\n\n### 6.2 Integration Tests\n\n**File**: `tests/integration/f005-status-and-logs.integration.test.js`\n\n| Test Case | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| Full Status Flow | Start pipeline → query status → verify all fields |\n| Log Pagination | Read logs with offset → verify pagination metadata |\n| Message Chunking | Long log → verify chunk splitting at line boundaries |\n| Heartbeat Flow | Start pipeline → wait for heartbeat → verify message |\n| Error Push | Trigger error → verify error summary push |\n\n### 6.3 Test Coverage Target\n\n- Core modules: > 90% branch coverage\n- All user stories covered by integration tests\n\n---\n\n## 7. Risk Assessment\n\n| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |\n|------|-------------|--------|------------|\n| Telegram API rate limiting | Medium | Medium | Implement message throttling, batch short messages |\n| Large log file memory usage | Low | High | Use stream reading with line counter |\n| Heartbeat thread blocking | Low | Medium | Use async intervals, no blocking calls |\n| Message send failures | Medium | Low | Retry queue with exponential backoff |\n| UTF-8 boundary issues | Low | Medium | Test with multi-byte characters, use string methods |\n\n---\n\n## 8. User Story to Component Mapping\n\n| User Story | Primary Component | Supporting Components |\n|------------|-------------------|----------------------|\n| US-1: Enhanced Status Aggregation | pipeline-status-aggregator.js | status.js, state-manager.js |\n| US-2: Paginated Log Retrieval | log-pager.js | logs.js, pipeline-controller.js |\n| US-3: Telegram Message Chunking | message-chunker.js | logs.js, status.js |\n| US-4: Heartbeat Progress Push | pipeline-notifier.js | pipeline-status-aggregator.js |\n| US-5: Error Summary Auto-Push | pipeline-notifier.js | pipeline-status-aggregator.js |\n| US-6: Diagnostic Error Handling | All components | formatter.js |\n\n---\n\n## 9. Implementation Phases\n\n### Phase 1: Foundation (T-001 ~ T-009)\n- Setup test infrastructure\n- Create message-chunker utility\n- Create log-pager utility\n\n### Phase 2: Core Services (T-010 ~ T-099)\n- Implement pipeline-status-aggregator\n- Enhance state-manager with error extraction\n- Create pipeline-notifier skeleton\n\n### Phase 3: User Story Implementation (T-100+)\n- US-1: Enhanced status command\n- US-2: Paginated logs command\n- US-3: Message chunking integration\n- US-4: Heartbeat push\n- US-5: Error auto-push\n- US-6: Diagnostic errors\n\n### Phase 4: Polish (T-900+)\n- Configuration documentation\n- Performance optimization\n- Edge case handling\n\n---\n\n## 10. Key Decisions\n\n| ID | Decision | Rationale |\n|----|----------|-----------|\n| D1 | Independent notifier service | Decouples push logic from execution, prevents blocking |\n| D2 | Line-based log pagination | More intuitive than byte offset, matches user mental model |\n| D3 | Line-boundary chunking | Preserves UTF-8 integrity, maintains readability |\n| D4 | Retry queue for failed sends | Resilience without blocking main flow |\n| D5 | Configurable heartbeat interval | Allows tuning based on pipeline duration |\n| D6 | Optional per-target notifications | Reduces noise for long pipelines |\n","file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/005-pipeline-status-and-log-streaming/plan.md"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":40390,"output_tokens":4702,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde7d5b3127935cc6935ad960a6b2","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:04:15.400Z","_requestId":"8c83b89fde8941858aa97e5b6b7114a4"}
