ine boundaries, (1/N) labels, no UTF-8 corruption (AC-3.1~3.3)\n  - **Complexity**: Low\n  - **US**: US-3\n\n- [ ] [T-109] Add file download option for very long logs — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js\n  - **Goal**: Offer file download for logs > 20000 chars\n  - **Input**: Long log content\n  - **Output**: Inline button to download full log as file\n  - **Acceptance**: Threshold at 20000 chars, file download works (AC-3.4)\n  - **Complexity**: Medium\n  - **US**: US-3\n\n### US-4: Heartbeat Progress Push\n\n- [ ] [T-110] Integrate notifier with pipeline start — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  - **Goal**: Call notifier.notifyStart when pipeline starts\n  - **Input**: Pipeline start event\n  - **Output**: Start notification sent to Telegram\n  - **Acceptance**: Push on daemon start, includes run ID and target count (AC-4.1)\n  - **Complexity**: Low\n  - **US**: US-4\n\n- [ ] [T-111] Start heartbeat when pipeline runs — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  - **Goal**: Start heartbeat interval on pipeline start\n  - **Input**: Pipeline type, interval config\n  - **Output**: Periodic heartbeat messages\n  - **Acceptance**: Heartbeat every N minutes, shows current target and progress (AC-4.2)\n  - **Complexity**: Low\n  - **US**: US-4\n\n- [ ] [T-112] Stop heartbeat and push final result — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  - **Goal**: Stop heartbeat and send completion message on pipeline end\n  - **Input**: Pipeline completion event\n  - **Output**: Final status summary\n  - **Acceptance**: Heartbeat stopped, final message with duration and results (AC-4.4)\n  - **Complexity**: Low\n  - **US**: US-4\n\n- [ ] [T-113] Add throttling for heartbeat pushes — file: src/services/pipeline-notifier.js\n  - **Goal**: Prevent rapid successive heartbeat messages\n  - **Input**: Heartbeat requests\n  - **Output**: Throttled messages\n  - **Acceptance**: Minimum interval between messages enforced (AC-4.5)\n  - **Complexity**: Low\n  - **US**: US-4\n\n### US-5: Error Summary Auto-Push\n\n- [ ] [T-114] Push error summary on target failure — file: src/services/pipeline-notifier.js\n  - **Goal**: Auto-push error summary when target execution fails\n  - **Input**: Error event with targetId, stage, message\n  - **Output**: Telegram message with error summary\n  - **Acceptance**: Auto-push enabled, includes targetId, stage, truncated error (AC-5.1, AC-5.2)\n  - **Complexity**: Medium\n  - **US**: US-5\n\n- [ ] [T-115] Push pipeline failure summary — file: src/services/pipeline-notifier.js\n  - **Goal**: Push summary when entire pipeline fails\n  - **Input**: Pipeline failure event\n  - **Output**: Summary with failed targets count, first error time, suggestion\n  - **Acceptance**: Shows failed count, first error time, suggested action (AC-5.3)\n  - **Complexity**: Low\n  - **US**: US-5\n\n- [ ] [T-116] Add \"view full log\" button — file: src/services/pipeline-notifier.js\n  - **Goal**: Add inline button for full error log viewing\n  - **Input**: Error context\n  - **Output**: Message with inline button that sends full log on click\n  - **Acceptance**: Button works, sends full log on callback (AC-5.4)\n  - **Complexity**: Medium\n  - **US**: US-5\n\n### US-6: Diagnostic Error Handling\n\n- [ ] [T-117] Standardize error response format — file: src/bot/commands/formatter.js\n  - **Goal**: Ensure all errors use consistent format\n  - **Input**: Various error types\n  - **Output**: Formatted error messages with emoji, type, details\n  - **Acceptance**: Format: `❌ 错误类型: 详情`, includes suggestion (AC-6.3, AC-6.4)\n  - **Complexity**: Low\n  - **US**: US-6\n\n- [ ] [T-118] Add file path to missing file errors — file: src/services/pipeline-status-aggregator.js, src/utils/log-pager.js\n  - **Goal**: Include file path in missing file error messages\n  - **Input**: File path that doesn't exist\n  - **Output**: Error message with full path\n  - **Acceptance**: Error includes file path, permission suggestion (AC-6.1)\n  - **Complexity**: Low\n  - **US**: US-6\n\n- [ ] [T-119] Add parse error details to state errors — file: src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js\n  - **Goal**: Return detailed error for state file parse failures\n  - **Input**: JSON parse error\n  - **Output**: Error with file path and parse error message\n  - **Acceptance**: Includes file path, parse error snippet (AC-6.2)\n  - **Complexity**: Low\n  - **US**: US-6\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Polish (T-900+)\n\n- [ ] [T-901] Add integration tests for F-005 — file: tests/integration/f005-status-and-logs.integration.test.js\n  - **Goal**: End-to-end testing of all F-005 features\n  - **Input**: Test pipeline execution scenarios\n  - **Output**: Passing integration tests\n  - **Acceptance**: All US covered, real Telegram API mock\n  - **Complexity**: Medium\n  - **US**: All\n\n- [ ] [T-902] Update documentation for notifier config — file: .env.example\n  - **Goal**: Document new notifier environment variables\n  - **Input**: NOTIFIER_* config options\n  - **Output**: Updated .env.example with comments\n  - **Acceptance**: All notifier options documented with defaults\n  - **Complexity**: Low\n  - **US**: US-4, US-5\n\n- [ ] [T-903] Performance test for large log files — file: tests/performance/log-pager.perf.test.js\n  - **Goal**: Verify performance with large log files (>10MB)\n  - **Input**: Large log files\n  - **Output**: Performance metrics\n  - **Acceptance**: Read time < 500ms for 10MB, no memory spike\n  - **Complexity**: Low\n  - **US**: US-2\n\n- [ ] [T-904] Add error recovery test scenarios — file: tests/integration/f005-error-recovery.test.js\n  - **Goal**: Test error handling edge cases\n  - **Input**: Various error scenarios\n  - **Output**: Passing error recovery tests\n  - **Acceptance**: All AC-6 scenarios covered\n  - **Complexity**: Medium\n  - **US**: US-6\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Parallelizable |\n|-------|-------|----------------|\n| Foundation (T-001~T-009) | 5 | T-001~T-004 can run in parallel |\n| Core Services (T-010~T-099) | 11 | T-010, T-015 can start in parallel |\n| User Stories (T-100+) | 16 | US-1, US-2, US-3 tasks can run in parallel |\n| Polish (T-900+) | 4 | T-902, T-903 can run in parallel |\n\n**Total Tasks**: 36\n**Estimated Sessions**: 8-12 Dev sessions\n","file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/005-pipeline-status-and-log-streaming/tasks.md"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":45170,"output_tokens":4416,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde7d5b3127935cc6935ad960a6b2","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:05:31.956Z","_requestId":"8c83b89fde8941858aa97e5b6b7114a4"}
