T-902 as required\n- Changelog update planned in T-903\n\n---\n\n### 5. 覆盖缺口 ⚠️ ISSUE FOUND\n\n| ID | Spec Requirement | Plan Coverage | Tasks Coverage | Gap |\n|----|------------------|---------------|----------------|-----|\n| GAP-1 | AC-4.2: \"每 N 个 feature 完成后推送进度更新\" | plan.md:152 shows `heartbeatInterval = 30s` (time-based) | T-131, T-132 implement time-based | **Spec AC not fully covered** |\n\n**Analysis**: AC-4.2 explicitly requires push **after N features complete** (event-based), but plan and tasks implement **time-based** heartbeat (every 30s). These are fundamentally different approaches.\n\n---\n\n### 6. 不一致性 ⚠️ ISSUE FOUND\n\n| ID | Location | Inconsistency | Severity |\n|----|----------|---------------|----------|\n| INC-3 | spec.md:135 vs tasks.md:83 | **Scope Violation**: spec.md line 135 states \"Pipeline 执行逻辑修改\" is **Out of Scope**, but T-133 says \"Add heartbeat start/stop hooks in pipeline startup\" modifying `pipeline-controller.js` | **HIGH** |\n\n---\n\n## 📊 Finding Summary\n\n| Severity | Count | IDs |\n|----------|-------|-----|\n| **CRITICAL** | 0 | — |\n| **HIGH** | 3 | AMB-2, INC-1, INC-3 |\n| **MEDIUM** | 3 | AMB-1, AMB-3, INC-2 |\n| **LOW** | 0 | — |\n\n---\n\n## 🚨 HIGH Severity Findings Detail\n\n### HIGH-1: Scope Boundary Violation (INC-3)\n- **Location**: `spec.md:135` vs `tasks.md:83`\n- **Issue**: Spec explicitly states \"Pipeline 执行逻辑修改\" is **Out of Scope**, but T-133 modifies `pipeline-controller.js` to add heartbeat hooks\n- **Impact**: Violates agreed scope, may introduce unintended coupling\n- **Recommendation**: \n  1. Either move T-133 implementation to a separate observer pattern that doesn't modify pipeline-controller\n  2. Or update spec.md Scope Boundaries to include \"minimal lifecycle hooks for notification\"\n\n### HIGH-2: NFR Reliability Gap (INC-1)\n- **Location**: `spec.md:107`\n- **Issue**: NFR-2 requires \"消息队列机制确保推送可靠性\" but plan/tasks show fire-and-forget async push\n- **Impact**: Push failures may lose notifications, violating reliability requirement\n- **Recommendation**: Add task to implement in-memory queue with retry logic, or explicitly relax NFR-2 in spec\n\n### HIGH-3: AC-4.2 Semantic Mismatch (AMB-2)\n- **Location**: `spec.md:63` vs `plan.md:151`\n- **Issue**: AC-4.2 says \"每 N 个 feature 完成后推送\" (event-based), but plan implements time-based interval (every 30s)\n- **Impact**: User story acceptance criteria not met; behavior differs from spec\n- **Recommendation**: Clarify with PM: either update AC-4.2 to \"每 N 秒\" or change implementation to feature-count trigger\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Verdict\n\n| Criterion | Status |\n|-----------|--------|\n| No CRITICAL findings | ✅ |\n| No HIGH findings | ❌ (3 found) |\n\n**Judgment**: **NEEDS FIXES** — Found 3 HIGH severity issues that should be resolved before implementation.\n\n---\n\n## 📤 COMPLETION_SIGNAL\n\n```\nTO: Coordinator\nFROM: Reviewer Agent\nPHASE: 4 (Cross-Check)\nFEATURE: F-005 (005-pipeline-status-and-log-streaming)\nVERDICT: NEEDS_FIXES\nFINDINGS:\n  - HIGH: INC-3 - Scope boundary violation (T-133 modifies pipeline-controller)\n  - HIGH: INC-1 - Missing message queue for NFR-2 reliability\n  - HIGH: AMB-2 - AC-4.2 event-based vs plan time-based mismatch\nACTION: Return to PM for spec/plan/tasks reconciliation\n```\n\n---\n\n**Next Steps**: Coordinator should route findings to PM for resolution before Dev implementation begins.\n\n[Agent ID: agent-975ce995]"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde81923008578a607f7ec3cc573c","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:07:33.716Z","_requestId":"8c83b89fde8941858aa97e5b6b7114a4"}
