pagination — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js\n  73→- [ ] [T-115] [US-2] Add integration test for paginated logs query — file: tests/integration/f005-status-and-logs.integration.test.js\n  74→\n  75→### US-3: Message Length Compliance\n  76→\n  77→- [ ] [T-121] [US-3] Implement message segment numbering ([1/3] format) — file: src/services/log-pager.js\n  78→- [ ] [T-122] [US-3] Add segment interval delay (500ms) to avoid rate limits — file: src/services/telegram-pusher.js\n  79→- [ ] [T-123] [US-3] Implement --file parameter in logs handler — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js\n  80→- [ ] [T-124] [US-3] Add integration test for message chunking — file: tests/integration/f005-status-and-logs.integration.test.js\n  81→\n  82→### US-4: Heartbeat Progress Push\n  83→\n  84→- [ ] [T-131] [US-4] Create heartbeat config loader — file: src/services/telegram-pusher.js\n  85→- [ ] [T-132] [US-4] Implement heartbeat progress message format — file: src/services/telegram-pusher.js\n  86→- [ ] [T-133] [US-4] Add minimal lifecycle hooks (onPipelineStart/onPipelineStop) to pipeline-controller — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  87→- [ ] [T-134] [US-4] Wire heartbeat pusher to lifecycle events from pipeline-controller — file: src/services/telegram-pusher.js\n  88→- [ ] [T-135] [US-4] Add HEARTBEAT_ENABLED, HEARTBEAT_FEATURE_COUNT config options — file: src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js\n  89→- [ ] [T-136] [US-4] Add integration test for event-based heartbeat with throttle — file: tests/integration/f005-status-and-logs.integration.test.js\n  90→\n  91→### US-5: Error Summary Push\n  92→\n  93→- [ ] [T-141] [US-5] Implement error summary message format — file: src/services/telegram-pusher.js\n  94→- [ ] [T-142] [US-5] Add error line extraction from log file — file: src/services/log-pager.js\n  95→- [ ] [T-143] [US-5] Implement silent mode for expected failures — file: src/services/telegram-pusher.js\n  96→- [ ] [T-144] [US-5] Add integration test for error sum