: .prizmkit/specs/REGISTRY.md\n 117→\n 118→---\n 119→\n 120→## Task Summary\n 121→\n 122→| Phase | Task Range | Count | Parallelizable |\n 123→|-------|------------|-------|----------------|\n 124→| Setup | T-001 ~ T-009 | 9 | 5 |\n 125→| Foundational | T-010 ~ T-042 | 33 | 0 |\n 126→| US-1 | T-101 ~ T-104 | 4 | 0 |\n 127→| US-2 | T-111 ~ T-115 | 5 | 0 |\n 128→| US-3 | T-121 ~ T-124 | 4 | 0 |\n 129→| US-4 | T-131 ~ T-136 | 6 | 0 |\n 130→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde86ad9a0ae1a9c5cf86c76a0ac0","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:18:37.926Z","_requestId":"8c83b89fde8941858aa97e5b6b7114a4"}
