d | Aliases | Description |\n  79→|---------|---------|-------------|\n  80→| `/pipeline` | `/p` | Manage pipelines (run/status/logs/stop) |\n  81→| `/bugfix` | `/b` | Start bugfix pipeline |\n  82→| `/planner` | — | Manage planner pipelines |\n  83→| `/status` | `/s` | Show running pipelines |\n  84→| `/logs` | `/l` | View pipeline logs |\n  85→| `/stop` | — | Stop running pipelines |\n  86→\n  87→### Verification\n  88→\n  89→- `npm test`: 105 tests pass (76 for F-002)\n  90→- Code review: PASS\n  91→- All 21 tasks completed\n  92→\n  93→---\n  94→\n  95→## F-003: Feature and Bug Plan Ingestion\n  96→\n  97→**Status:** completed  \n  98→**Completion Date:** 2026-03-12\n  99→\n 100→### Deliverables\n 101→\n 102→- `src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js` - Schema validation, version management, plan registry\n 103→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/plan.js` - Plan command handler (status/versions/use/rollback/validate)\n 104→- `src/bot/telegram.js` - Document upload handler for JSON files\n 105→- `src/services/pipeline-control-service.js` - Extended with resolvePlanListPath()\n 106→- `src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js` - Extended with plansDir config\n 107→- `plans/` directory structure with feature-list/ and bug-fix-list/ subdirectories\n 108→- Unit tests in `tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js`\n 109→- Integration tests in `tests/integration/f003-plan-ingestion.integration.test.js`\n 110→\n 111→### Acceptance Criteria Met\n 112→\n 113→- US-1: Upload Plan File - Telegram document message handling with auto-type detection\n 114→- US-2: Schema Validation - Ajv-based validation with field-level error messages\n 115→- US-3: Version Management - Timestamp-based versioning with use/rollback commands\n 116→- US-4: Plan Status Query - Status command showing version info and content summary\n 117→- US-5: Plan Integrity Protection - Validation precedes save, current version preserved on error\n 118→- US-6: Pipeline Integration - resolvePlanListPath() for dynamic plan path resolution\n 119→\n 120→### Commands Implemented\n 121→\n 122→| Command | Subcommands | Description |\n 123→|---------|-------------|-------------|\n 124→| `/plan` | status, versions, use, rollback, validate | Manage plan files |\n 125→\n 126→### Verification\n 127→\n 128→- Code review: PASS_WITH_WARNINGS\n 129→- All 18 tasks completed\n 130→- Unit tests: 19 passing\n 131→- Integration tests: 10 passing\n 132→\n 133→---\n 134→\n 135→## F-004: Pipeline Process Controller\n 136→\n 137→**Status:** completed\n 138→**Completion Date:** 2026-03-12\n 139→\n 140→### Deliverables\n 141→\n 142→- `src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js` - File-based lock management with PID validation\n 143→- `src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js` - State file reading/writing for daemon and pipeline state\n 144→- `src/pipeline-infra/error-codes.js` - Extended with 6 new error codes for F-004\n 145→- `src/pipeline-infra/path-policy.js` - Extended with lock/state path resolvers\n 146→- `src/services/pipeline-controller.js` - Unified pipeline control API with concurrency protection\n 147→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/pipeline.js` - Updated to use pipeline-controller\n 148→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js` - Updated to use pipeline-controller\n 149→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js` - Updated to use pipeline-controller\n 150→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/stop.js` - Updated to use pipeline-controller\n 151→- Unit tests in `tests/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.test.js` and `tests/pipeline-infra/state-manager.test.js`\n 152→- Unit tests in `tests/services/pipeline-controller.test.js`\n 153→- Integration tests in `tests/integration/f004-pipeline-controller.integration.test.js`\n 154→\n 155→### Acceptance Criteria Met\n 156→\n 157→- US-1: Unified Pipeline Start - startPipeline with daemon/foreground modes, lock acquisition\n 158→- US-2: Pipeline Stop - stopPipeline with ALREADY_STOPPED handling, lock release\n 159→- US-3: Target Retry - retryTarget with validation and mode support\n 160→- US-4: Run 