{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312042146ec36a06f70ae47cc","session_id":"5a4189c6-c669-4ea4-8c81-fee95bc26849","message":{"id":"20260312042146ec36a06f70ae47cc","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All F-005 tasks have been completed successfully. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## F-005: Pipeline Status Aggregation and Log Streaming - Implementation Summary\n\n### New Modules Created\n1. **`src/services/status-aggregator.js`** - Aggregates state from multiple sources (daemon meta, pipeline state, current session, last result) for unified status view\n2. **`src/services/log-pager.js`** - Paginated log reading with streaming support for large files (>1MB), error line extraction\n3. **`src/services/telegram-pusher.js`** - Telegram message pushing with throttling (30s), chunking (4000 chars), heartbeat, retry logic (max 3, exponential backoff)\n\n### Updated Handlers\n- **`src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js`** - Enhanced with `--type=feature|bugfix` parameter, uses status-aggregator for aggregated status\n- **`src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js`** - Enhanced with `--lines=N`, `--offset=N`, `--type=feature|bugfix`, `--file` parameters\n\n### Key Features Implemented\n| User Story | Feature |\n|------------|---------|\n| US-1 | Aggregated status query with running/paused/completed/failed/idle states |\n| US-2 | Paginated logs with configurable lines (max 500) and offset |\n| US-3 | Auto-chunking at 4000 chars with [N/M] segment numbering, 500ms segment delay |\n| US-4 | Event-driven heartbeat with 30s throttle via pipeline-controller lifecycle hooks |\n| US-5 | Error summary push with log lines and execution duration |\n| US-6 | Diagnostic error messages for missing/corrupted state files |\n\n### Test Coverage\n- Unit tests: `tests/services/status-aggregator.test.js`, `tests/services/log-pager.test.js`, `tests/services/telegram-pusher.test.js`\n- Integration tests: `tests/integration/f005-status-and-logs.integration.test.js`\n- All tests pass with exit code 0\n\n### Documentation Updated\n- `.prizm-docs/runtime/services.prizm` - Added new modules and APIs\n- `.prizm-docs/runtime/bot.prizm` - Updated command interfaces\n- `.prizm-docs/changelog.prizm` - Added F-005 entries\n- `.prizmkit/specs/REGISTRY.md` - Added F-005 completion record"}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":126153,"output_tokens":539,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde86ad9a0ae1a9c5cf86c76a0ac0","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:21:57.756Z","_requestId":"8c83b89fde8941858aa97e5b6b7114a4"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"646810da-8e80-4ac8-a49a-c500ae70af3c","session_id":"5a4189c6-c669-4ea4-8c81-fee95bc26849","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde86ad9a0ae1a9c5cf86c76a0ac0","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All F-005 tasks have been completed successfully. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## F-005: Pipeline Status Aggregation and Log Streaming - Implementation Summary\n\n### New Modules Created\n1. **`src/services/status-aggregator.js`** - Aggregates state from multiple sources (daemon meta, pipeline state, current session, last result) for unified status view\n2. **`src/services/log-pager.js`** - Paginated log reading with streaming support for large files (>1MB), error line extraction\n3. **`src/services/telegram-pusher.js`** - Telegram message pushing with throttling (30s), chunking (4000 chars), heartbeat, retry logic (max 3, exponential backoff)\n\n### Updated Handlers\n- **`src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js`** - Enhanced with `--type=feature|bugfix` parameter, uses status-aggregator for aggregated status\n- **`src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js`** - Enhanced with `--lines=N`, `--offset=N`, `--type=feature|bugfix`, `--file` parameters\n\n### Key Features Implemented\n| User Story | Feature |\n|------------|---------|\n| US-1 | Aggregated status query with running/paused/completed/failed/idle states |\n| US-2 | Paginated logs with configurable lines (max 500) and offset |\n| US-3 | Auto-chunking at 4000 chars with [N/M] segment numbering, 500ms segment delay |\n| US-4 | Event-driven heartbeat with 30s throttle via pipeline-controller lifecycle hooks |\n| US-5 | Error summary push with log lines and execution duration |\n| US-6 | Diagnostic error messages for missing/corrupted state files |\n\n### Test Coverage\n- Unit tests: `tests/services/status-aggregator.test.js`, `tests/services/log-pager.test.js`, `tests/services/telegram-pusher.test.js`\n- Integration tests: `tests/integration/f005-status-and-logs.integration.